headline: 2 Dividend Stocks to Double Up on Right Now
summary: PepsiCo's stock has tumbled despite it being a Dividend King and making growth-oriented investments.  Hershey is going to have horrible earnings in 2025, but it hasn't stopped growing its business.  Emotions on Wall Street tend to swing like a pendulum, going from far too excited to far too pessimistic.
